{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"貢獻 MDN","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"\n  <ol>\n    <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/About\">關於 MDN</a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>貢獻 MDN</summary>\n            <ol>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Getting_started\">開始入門 MDN</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute\">貢獻 MDN</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Howto\">Things you can do</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Localize\">Localizing MDN</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Guidelines\">MDN 內容與風格指南</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Structures\">Content structures</a></li>\n             </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>歡迎！當你在看這個頁面時，就已經邁向成為 MDN 貢獻者的第一步！</p>\n<p>這份指南涵蓋貢獻 MDN 的各個面向，包括風格指引、使用編輯器和工具的引導……等等。在編輯或建立任何頁面前，請先閱讀並確認同意 <a href=\"https://www.mozilla.org/zh-TW/about/legal/terms/mozilla/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Mozilla 網站與通訊使用條款</a>。</p>\n<p>如果之前你並沒有貢獻過 MDN 的話，<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Getting_started\">開始入門</a>指南能幫你決定要投入的任務。</p><div class=\"row topicpage-table\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <div class=\"section\" id=\"sect2\"><dl><dl><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"how-to_guides\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Howto\">How-to guides</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\">這些文章將會帶領你一步步完成貢獻 MDN 專案所需完成的目標</dd><dt class=\"landingPageList\" id=\"開始入門_mdn\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute/Getting_started\">開始入門 MDN</a></dt><dd class=\"landingPageList\">這是一個開放的開發者和作家社區，不分品牌、瀏覽器、平台，為更好的 Web 構建提供更多資源。每個人都能做出貢獻，而每個貢獻者的付出都讓我們變得更為壯大。要想持續推動 Web 創新、成就更為偉大的事物？就讓我們和您一起，從這裡開始。</dd></dl></dl></div>\n    <div class=\"section\" id=\"sect3\"><dl><dt <=\"\" dl=\"\" id=\"sect4\"></dt></dl></div>\n    </div>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"歡迎！當你在看這個頁面時，就已經邁向成為 MDN 貢獻者的第一步！","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Beitragen zu MDN","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Contributing to MDN","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Contribuir a MDN","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Contribuer à MDN","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"MDN への貢献","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"MDN에 참여하기","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Contributing to MDN","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Contribuindo para o MDN","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Участие в развитии MDN","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"为 MDN 做贡献","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/mdn/contribute","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/mdn/contribute/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/MDN","title":"MDN 專案"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/MDN/Contribute","title":"貢獻 MDN"}],"pageTitle":"貢獻 MDN - MDN 專案 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}